title: DrugMatrix Pathology Images
description: The DrugMatrixÂ® database is a unique toxicogenomic reference database that contains data on over 600 drugs, chemicals, toxicants, and biochemical reagents. These compounds have been extensively curated and profiled using large-scale gene expression analysis as well as pharmacologic activity (MDS Pharma assays) and in-life evaluations, including haematology, clinical chemistry and histopathology. This is the dataset of histopathology images with links to ChEMBL DrugMatrix entries.
